</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>首款 Windows 電腦 5nm 製程處理器   Qualcomm Snapdragon 8cx Gen 3 發表</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/01/06/qualcomm-snapdragon-8cx-gen-3/notebook/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=qualcomm-snapdragon-8cx-gen-3</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[唐美鳳]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jan 2022 03:20:03 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[流動電腦]]></category><category><![CDATA[qualcomm]]></category><category><![CDATA[Snapdragon 8cx Gen 3]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1079836</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>晶片生產商 Qualcomm 昨日在 CES 2022 發表了，適用於高階 Windows 筆電的 Snapdragon 8cx Gen 3 處理器，廠方聲稱 CPU 和 GPU 效能分別有最高 85% 和 60% 的提升。Snapdragon 8cx Gen 3 採用 5nm 製程，是首款採用這工藝的 Windows 筆電處理器，相關筆電產品預計今年上半年推出。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>晶片生產商 Qualcomm 昨日在 CES 2022 發表了，適用於高階 Windows 筆電的 Snapdragon 8cx Gen 3 處理器，廠方聲稱 CPU 和 GPU 效能分別有最高 85% 和 60% 的提升。Snapdragon 8cx Gen 3 採用 5nm 製程，是首款採用這工藝的 Windows 筆電處理器，相關筆電產品預計今年上半年推出。</p><p><span id="more-1079836"></span></p><p>Snapdragon 8cx Gen 3 支援最高 120fps 的全高清遊戲，並進行了針對性改善，令用戶可以獲得比其他處理器將 50% 的遊戲時間。處理器配備 Spectra ISP，令視像鏡頭的啟動時間快 15%，同時支援自動對焦、自動白平衡和自動曝光，亦支援 4K HDR 攝錄和最多 4 個鏡頭。加上擁有雜噪和回音消除技術，令音效在任何環境都更清晰。</p><p>Snapdragon 8cx Gen 3 提供 29+ TOPS 的人工智能加速，是其他處理器的約 3 倍。其安全處理單元內建 Microsft Pluton 解決方案，可以直接安全地儲存敏感數據、憑證和加密密鑰等，亦支援 Windows Hello 安全框架和儲存加密。此外，Snapdragon 8cx Gen 3 還能夠支援 Snapdragon X55、X62 和 X65 Modem，令筆電可以連接 5G 網絡，而 FastConnect 6900 則支援 Microsoft 的 Wi-Fi Dual Station 和 Qualcomm 自家 4 流雙頻同步技術，實現 Wi-Fi 6/6E 速度之餘，更能夠在 4G、5G 和 Wi-Fi 6/6E 之間無縫切換。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://mspoweruser.com/qualcomm-snapdragon-8cx-gen-3-improved-performance/">mspoweruser</a></p>
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=TsR-yjLswik:aYGGx_n2kbw:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=TsR-yjLswik:aYGGx_n2kbw:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>銀聯超閃優惠&lt;br/&gt;雲閃付 App 一站式點餐+充電+繳費</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/01/06/union-pay-food-republic/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=union-pay-food-republic</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[藍骨]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jan 2022 03:00:45 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[優惠]]></category><category><![CDATA[銀聯]]></category><category><![CDATA[銀聯銀閃付]]></category><category><![CDATA[電子付款]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1076178</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>現在市面上電子付款工具多如繁星，不過真正可以配合日常生活需要，帶來便利的卻不是很多。銀聯雲閃付 App 就結合了各種生活便利功能，最近更有不少優惠，我們就來實試一下到底如何善用這個 App 吧！</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>現在市面上電子支付工具多如繁星，不過真正能配合日常生活需要，帶來便利的卻不是很多。雲閃付 App 就結合了各種生活便利功能，最近更有不少優惠，我們就來實試一下到底如何善用這個 App 吧。<br /><span id="more-1076178"></span></p><h2>聯乘大食代優惠</h2><p>香港人每日面對的其中一大難題，就是要在時間有限的 Lunch Time 到餐廳先等位、後落單、再等上菜、食完再跑回 Office 繼續工作。試想如果可以同步幾個步驟，至少應該可以縮減一些時間，那 Lunch Time 就可以相對輕鬆一點。今次歌儀就試用了雲閃付 App，實測是否真的可以節省食飯落單時間。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1076276" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_00_14_01.Still012.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="844" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_00_14_01.Still012.jpg 1500w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_00_14_01.Still012-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_00_14_01.Still012-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_00_14_01.Still012-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" />▲ 今次跟雲閃付 App 聯乘的大食代在香港幾個商場都有分店</p><p>歌儀首先拍下大食代 Food Court 的落單 QR 二維碼，在網上就可以預先落單，付款的時候選擇使用銀聯，就會自動開啓雲閃付 App，付款相當輕鬆。而就算去到現場才選擇吃什麼，同樣可以用銀聯二維碼付款。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1076294" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unionpay_2.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="998" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unionpay_2.jpg 1500w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unionpay_2-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unionpay_2-1280x852.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unionpay_2-768x511.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" />▲ 用相機 App 或者其他 QR 掃描器都可以</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1078525 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269820070_623304668940591_5053910201130152686_n.jpg" alt="" width="1170" height="659" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269820070_623304668940591_5053910201130152686_n.jpg 1170w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269820070_623304668940591_5053910201130152686_n-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/269820070_623304668940591_5053910201130152686_n-768x433.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" />▲ 選擇銀聯付款就可以選用雲閃付 App 支付再享用優惠</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1076282" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_00_18_13.Still013-1.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="844" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_00_18_13.Still013-1.jpg 1500w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_00_18_13.Still013-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_00_18_13.Still013-1-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_00_18_13.Still013-1-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" />▲ 不論網上落單還是實際到場付款都可獲折扣</p><p>當然，對於香港人來說最重要的還是優惠。今次雲閃付 App 聯乘大食代提供的優惠有兩個，用雲閃付掃描 QR 二維碼點餐滿 $40 就減 $10 ，或於收銀機點餐用銀聯二維碼付款就滿 $40 減 $5。這樣計起來當然是雲閃付掃描 QR 點餐更抵。由於反應熱烈，有關優惠活動已延長至 <span lang="EN-US">2 </span>月 <span lang="EN-US">28 </span>日，大家食飯可以繼續慳錢又慳時間。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1076284" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_00_32_12.Still009.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="844" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_00_32_12.Still009.jpg 1500w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_00_32_12.Still009-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_00_32_12.Still009-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_00_32_12.Still009-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" />▲ 不用排隊跟別人迫，直接落單輕鬆方便</p><h2>生活優惠貼心</h2><p>生活當然唔止食飯！現代人出門都是機不離手，手機沒電就相當不便。雲閃付 App 亦於 App 內提供了 ChargeSpot 充電租借服務。現在在 App 內點選服務並經雲閃付支付租借按金，就可以獲得 3 張 1 小時免費充電券，就算在外也不用煩惱手機沒電了。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1076290" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_01_27_24.Still003.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="844" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_01_27_24.Still003.jpg 1500w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_01_27_24.Still003-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_01_27_24.Still003-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_01_27_24.Still003-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" />▲ 登記即送免費充電券，隨時可以使用</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1076289" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_01_23_02.Still004.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="844" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_01_23_02.Still004.jpg 1500w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_01_23_02.Still004-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_01_23_02.Still004-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_01_23_02.Still004-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" />▲ 用餐之時，正好可以讓手機充電</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1076291" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_01_32_08.Still002.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="844" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_01_32_08.Still002.jpg 1500w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_01_32_08.Still002-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_01_32_08.Still002-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/union_pay.00_01_32_08.Still002-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" />▲ 各種功能覆蓋生活不同範疇</p><p>除此之外，雲閃付 App 本身也可以進行各種日常生活開支繳費，例如交電費、煤氣費、管理費等等，部分繳費更可以儲信用卡積分。最近更開通了港康碼的申請服務，隨時經雲閃付 App 都可以申請到。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1077418 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/268420447_1033064923920992_6632656199218607433_n-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/268420447_1033064923920992_6632656199218607433_n-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/268420447_1033064923920992_6632656199218607433_n-415x900.png 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/268420447_1033064923920992_6632656199218607433_n-768x1664.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/268420447_1033064923920992_6632656199218607433_n-709x1536.png 709w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/268420447_1033064923920992_6632656199218607433_n-945x2048.png 945w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/268420447_1033064923920992_6632656199218607433_n.png 738w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲ 在雲閃付 App 內就可以處理各種賬單繳費</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1076295" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unionpay_3.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="998" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unionpay_3.jpg 1500w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unionpay_3-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unionpay_3-1280x852.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unionpay_3-768x511.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p></p><div class="feedflare">
